y different that there is no way having a strict way of prayer would work. Me, being a high school student would not appreciate it. I am not religious, but have no problem with people that are. If you want prayer every day in schools…GO TO A PRIVATE CHRISTIAN SCHOOL!! "/><type4:DocumentMetaData xmi:id="13" sofa="1" begin="0" end="576" language="en" documentId="1742" isLastSegment="false"/><types:WebArgumentMetadata xmi:id="24" sofa="1" begin="0" end="0" author="Magnolia" date="05/24/2010 12:46 PM" docType="artcomment" origUrl="http://www.forerunner.com/forerunner/X0098_Ban_on_school_prayer.html#c001662" topic="prayer-in-schools" thumbsUp="0" thumbsDown="0" origId="1742" notes="" title="Banning Prayer in Public Schools Has Led to America's Demise"/><type6:Paragraph xmi:id="39" sofa="1" begin="0" end="576"/><cas:View sofa="1" members="13 24 39"/></xmi:XMI>